Interface MvcResult


  • public interface MvcResult
    Provides access to the result of an executed request.

    3.2
    Author:
    Rossen Stoyanchev

      • getAsyncResult

        Object getAsyncResult()
        Get the result of asynchronous execution or null if concurrent handling did not start. This method will hold and await the completion of concurrent handling.
        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - if concurrent handling does not complete within the allocated async timeout value.

      • getAsyncResult

        Object getAsyncResult(long timeout)
        Get the result of asynchronous execution or null if concurrent handling did not start. This method will wait for up to the given timeout for the completion of concurrent handling.
        Parameters:
        timeout - how long to wait for the async result to be set in milliseconds; if -1, the wait will be as long as the async timeout set on the Servlet request
